|style="background:brown"|Works Car
|?
|1919
|N/A
|Originally a 4ft gauge Bradford double decker, bought by Sheffield during WW2 to replace bombed trams. Converted to water carrying car/rail grinder. Currently Out of Service following an incident with Leeds 180.
